WeatherWise: Your Personalized Weather Companion

Stay ahead of the weather with WeatherWise! This intuitive app provides real-time weather updates and forecasts for your chosen city. With beautifully designed icons that represent various weather conditions—sunny, cloudy, rainy, and snowy—you can easily plan your day. Simply type in your city, hit "Enter," and get instant access to current temperatures, detailed descriptions, and a 5-day forecast. Enjoy a seamless user experience with animated icons that bring your weather to life. Whether you're planning a sunny day out or preparing for a rainy afternoon, WeatherWise has you covered
